load PreCSG
select Box_1 Cylinder_1 Sphere_1

section Intersection CSG Intersection 
state video on

caption .5 .15 3 This icon combines the selected models using CSG Intersection
highlight CombineCSGIntersectionIcon 3 0
wait 2

caption .5 .15 3 Click it to form the intersection of all selected models
state cursor on
moveover CombineCSGIntersectionIcon 1
click
wait 2

caption .5 .15 3 Note that in this case the intersection is very small
wait 3

moveover UndoIcon 1
click
wait 2
